sellerCard.oneLiner: When your software looks good, you looks good too
sellerCard.description: I am a Fullstack Developer with over a decade of experience in designing and delivering enterprise grade solutions. I specialize in fullstack development using Python, Node JS, and PHP, with a strong focus on AI systems, including computer vision and machine learning. My expertise lies in building scalable, efficient systems and solving complex challenges with innovative solutions. Known for my strategic problem solving and results driven approach, I am passionate about leveraging technology to create impactful outcomes and drive success.

description.content:
Hello there,

I am proficient and creative full stack website and app developer with a strong history in web development, website application and mobile application, script development and in building innovative systems. I am expert in all aspects of Front End web Development, Back End Development, Mern Stack Development.


MY EXPERTISE

  • Database (Mysql, Postgres, MongoDB)
  • PYTHON (Flask, OpenCV, MqTT, RabbitMQ, Computer Vision,Machine Learning)
  • NODE JS (Express JS, Adonis JS)
  • HTML5, CSS, Bootstrap, Javascript, JQuery, Tailwind Css
  • PHP (Laravel, Symfony, CodeIgnitor, Core PHP)
  • FrontEnd (Vuejs, NuxtJS)
  • SOCKET
  • ELECTRON
  • DOCKER
  • Deployment (AWS , Azure, GCloud, Digitalocean, Kubernetes)
  • Payment Integrations (Paypal, Stripe, Square,Authorise.net, PayUMoney, RazorPay,Cashfree)
  • Email & SMS (Mailchimp, Sendgrid, Twilio)
  • Social Login (Facebook, Google, Twitter, Linkedin, Instagram)


WHAT I OFFER

  • WELL STRUCTURED CODE
  • DATABASE INTEGRATION
  • REST API DEVELOPMENT
  • THIRD-PARTY API INTEGRATIONS
  • CODE DEBUGGING AND OPTIMIZATION
  • CUSTOM APPLICATION
  • CROSS BROWSER COMPATIBILITY


Note:- 

Please contact me before placing the order so that we can discuss and make something awesome together.


Full Stack Developer
